{"word":"H7679 - שָׂגָא - sâgâʼ - saw-gaw' - Increase","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׂגָא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>sâgâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>saw-gaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Increase"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பெருகு, அதிகமாகு, மகிமைப்படுத்து, பெருகப்பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to increase, to grow, to magnify, to grow great (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to make great"},{"paragraph":"2) to magnify, to laud"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>grow</i>, that is, (causatively) to <i>enlarge</i>, (figuratively) <i>laud: - </i>increase, magnify."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7679 - שָׂגָא - sâgâʼ - saw-gaw'/7679\">H7679</a>, <a href=\"#/H7685 - שָׂגָה - sâgâh - saw-gaw'/7685\">H7685</a>, <a href=\"#/H7689 - שַׂגִּיא - saggîyʼ - sag-ghee'/7689\">H7689</a>"}]}